<div class="full-story-head">
<h1>Controversial DRS to be used in 2015 ICC World Cup</h1>
<h2 class="iplfstoryh2cls"><p>Cricket's world governing body, International Cricket Council (ICC) confirmed that the controversial Decision Review System (DRS) will be used during the ICC World Cup 2015.</p>
</h2> 	</div>
        <div class="writer">
        
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
 Last Updated: Thursday, January 29, 2015 - 08:52</div>


